  "body": "**Is your feature request related to a problem? Please describe.**\r\nWe are trying to monitor the state of our Blockchain by comparing the last hash of each node. This would allow us to detect inconsistencies in the network.\r\nNethermind comes with a set of metrics exported in Prometheus format. The number of the last block is available (`nethermind_blockchain_height`) but not its hash.\r\n\r\n**Describe the solution you'd like**\r\nExport the hash of the last block in the section `Blockchain` of metrics https://docs.nethermind.io/monitoring/metrics/#blockchain.\r\n\r\n**Describe alternatives you've considered**\r\nWe considered fetching the hash of the last block through RPC calls but it is not possible in our context since we are using Grafana to display metrics and trigger alerts.\r\n\r\n**Additional context**\r\nRelated PR https://github.com/NethermindEth/nethermind/pull/6498\r\n",
